      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMICAL WARREN (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (30.23) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning seven races. Can make amends. ZIPPING LIPA (5) was well back throughout but attacked the line to hit the frame when a 2.5 lengths second (30.00) at this track in Grade 4/5. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from three starts. Expected to be in this for a long way. CANYA DYNAMITE (6) struggled in tougher grade last start after drifting back at this track, but prior to that won by 2.5 lengths at this track (29.89) beating Zipping Urban in a Grade 5 on May 21. Better than last start and can bounce back. DAYSEA'S CHIEF (2) can measure up with the right run.",
